347
00:47:18,424 --> 00:47:20,843
I turned in my weapon and my badge.

348
00:47:24,138 --> 00:47:25,222
Good luck.

349
00:47:26,640 --> 00:47:27,641
Colonel...

350
00:47:30,644 --> 00:47:31,729
I'm sorry.

351
00:47:38,778 --> 00:47:41,781
Men like me would give our lives
to arrest a man like him.

352
00:47:46,035 --> 00:47:47,453
You did everything right, Peña.

353
00:47:49,080 --> 00:47:51,207
But now you're all alone.

354
00:48:22,947 --> 00:48:25,074
We need to talk about your security.

355
00:48:27,410 --> 00:48:28,911
Let me be in charge.

356
00:48:30,788 --> 00:48:32,206
