360
00:49:29,013 --> 00:49:31,348
-They got Gilberto.
<i>-I don't understand.</i>

361
00:49:31,515 --> 00:49:34,226
I thought Gilberto
had this all under control.

362
00:49:34,602 --> 00:49:35,769
<i>So did I.</i>

363
00:49:37,980 --> 00:49:38,981
And what now?

364
00:49:39,565 --> 00:49:40,941
<i>This could get messy.</i>

365
00:49:41,108 --> 00:49:44,111
